read -rd '' disclaimer <<EOM
\n\033[1;91mWARNING:\033[0;1m READ BEFORE CONTINUING:\033[0m\n\n

This script is in no way affiliated with, endorsed, nor supported by KONAMI. In order to access the full game outside\n
